# game/room.rpy:557
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_7206a21e:

    # ermy_game "This thought is nothing new to me. In fact, it’s what I wake up to every single morning... I must admit it’s a rather disappointing thought, almost as much as waking up hungry."
    ermy_game "這個想法對我來並不新鮮。實際上，每個早上我一起來就會想到它……必須承認這是一個相當讓人失望的想法，幾乎就像餓著肚子醒來一樣。"

# game/room.rpy:558
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0c6cbe2c:

    # ermy_game "Yes, hungry, as it tries to devour me day by day, to no avail. I never retaliate, yet it always stops after the first bite – I probably taste awful, like a sour grape."
    ermy_game "是的，飢餓試圖吞噬我的每一天，反抗都是徒勞的，我也從不這樣做，但總是在嘗過一口之后就停止——因為味道嘗起來很糟糕，就像一顆酸葡萄。"

# game/room.rpy:559
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a4a2a2bf:

    # ermy_game "I’ve been here, I’ve been there, I’ve been in between. I don’t believe in aliens, yet I always feel like one. Where am I supposed to be then? If only I knew... If only they knew. No one does, seriously, it’s just some people are ridiculously good at hiding the obvious."
    ermy_game "我在這裡，我在那裡，我介於兩者之間。我不相信有外星人，但我總覺得自己是。那我應該在哪裡呢?如果我知道……或是他們知道就好了。沒人知道，說真的，人們太善於掩飾了。"

# game/room.rpy:560
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_7c897ab3:

    # ermy_game "After some time, I decided to change my strategy and get rid of every single thought appearing in my feverish mind. Completely, entirely, eternally. After some time, I found the best solution to do so – something which I called 'mindless living', as opposed to this mindfulness nonsense, oh so popular among the masses."
    ermy_game "過了段時間后，我決定改變我的策略，擺脫每一個出現在我瘋狂的腦海中的想法，完全的、全部的、永遠的。這之后，我找到了最好的解決辦法——我稱之為\"盲目的生活\"，而不是在社會主流思想裡胡言亂語。"

# game/room.rpy:561
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_3f6d0e8b:

    # ermy_game "Mindless living is easy – you simply need to be dead tired all the time. I mean, when you’re exhausted, you don’t want to think, you want to sleep. In a way, I decided to go through an inverted Maslow pyramid."
    ermy_game "盲目的生存是很容易，你隻需要操勞一生直到死亡就行。我的意思是，當你筋疲力盡，不想思考，而隻想睡覺的那個時候。在某種程度上，這種狀態就像穿過一個倒置的馬斯洛金字塔 。"

# game/room.rpy:562
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_262eda81:

    # ermy_game "Strangely enough, soon my body got used to being deprived of sleep. I drastically cut down my calorie intake as a next step – this also allowed me to become quite slim, it concentrated me, one hundred percent, on food and food only, regardless of how tired I was. Meat. Fish. Pasta. Pizza. I could smell each of these words…"
    ermy_game "奇怪的是，我的身體很快地適應失眠的狀態。然后我下一步大幅降低攝入的熱量——這樣也讓我變得苗條。無論我多麼困，這也讓我把100％的注意力集中到食物上來。肉、魚、意大利面、披薩，我仿佛能聞到它們的味道……"

# game/room.rpy:563
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0d361a10:

    # ermy_game "I’m not a monk or anything, so limiting myself that much became problematic – my stupid body craved sleep and food. \"Feed me! Get me some rest!\""
    ermy_game "我終究不是一個修行之人，因此控制自己變得越來越難。我愚蠢的身體想要休息與食物。\"喂飽我! 讓我休息一下!\""

# game/room.rpy:564
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ca1fddb6:

    # ermy_game "Every time I succumbed to that voice of reason, I ate until I was about to blow up, and then I could sleep for a day or so, only to wake up and think…"
    ermy_game "每次當我屈服於那個想法時，我就會胡吃海喝，然后睡一整天的覺，直到醒來又開始思考。"

# game/room.rpy:565
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_c645354f:

    # ermy_game "I’m not supposed to be here."
    ermy_game "我不應該在這裡。"

# game/room.rpy:566
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9453a70e:

    # ermy_game "I realized I struggle that much because I probably lack training – after all, I thought, my mindless living should be treated not only as a clever invention, but also as a skill to develop. I decided to pursue a career in it, and shortly after I found my dream job. It was the number one in my shortlist – in fact, it got me enlisted."
    ermy_game "那時候我發現我之所以這麼痛苦是因為自己缺少鍛煉。畢竟，我想，我盲目的生存不應該隻被認為是一個聰明的發現，而也應作為一種發展的技能。我下了決心在盲目生存的同時追求一份事業，過了不久，我找到了一份理想的工作。這份工作在我願望清單中是第一名。實際上，它把我招募了。"

# game/room.rpy:567
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_1569ca4b:

    # ermy_game "Yes, I joined the army."
    ermy_game "沒錯，我參軍了。"

# game/room.rpy:568
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_fa1459c8:

    # ermy_game "However, they fed me so well at the training camp that my silly mind decided to think again. So annoying, I’m telling you! And there was no stopping it… A phone started to ring in my head from time to time, driving me crazy. I know that as soon as I pick it up, I’d hear the same phrase…"
    ermy_game "可是，當我在軍訓營的時候，衣食無憂又讓我的腦子開始胡思亂想了。真糟糕！一旦開始想了，就沒法停止。就像電話在我腦海裡響不停。我知道如果我接起這個電話，就會聽到……"

# game/room.rpy:569
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_c78d7157:

    # ermy_game "\"Hey! I don’t think you’re supposed to be here.\""
    ermy_game "\"嘿！我不覺得你不應該在這裡。\""

# game/room.rpy:570
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_27b2a2e0:

    # ermy_game "That’s why, as soon as I could, I asked to be moved away from a grass-fed heaven of a military base to a wild, stinky battlefield."
    ermy_game "所以我盡快要求把我從和平的軍訓營調到狂野、惡臭的戰場。"

# game/room.rpy:571
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0ad26923:

    # ermy_game "Codename Hermes, that was my new name. Have you ever heard of a soldier named Ermy? Well, me neither."
    ermy_game "我的代號是赫耳墨斯。你聽說過叫葉爾米的軍人嗎？對了，我也沒有。"

# game/room.rpy:572
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5dd606d2:

    # ermy_game "I’ve been the happiest man on planet Earth since my first deployment, but then it ended with a buzz – at least that’s what I last heard, the buzz of a bullet, before it got so dark and lonely around me."
    ermy_game "從我第一次軍隊部署以來，我一直認為自己是全世界最開心的人。可是，后來直到我最后聽到子彈的嗡嗡聲，我周圍突然變得寂靜黑暗。"

# game/room.rpy:573
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_bc80c965:

    # ermy_game "Darkness gave way to a white tube of light that sucked me in like a vacuum. What a strange place that was – going all the way up to somewhere above the clouds, I could’ve sworn I saw familiar faces, faces of people long gone from this world."
    ermy_game "黑暗中出現一束白色的光，它像真空一樣把我吸了進去。這是一個多麼奇怪的地方啊——一直走到雲層之上的某個地方，我敢發誓我看到了熟悉的面孔，那些早已離開這個世界的人的面孔。"

# game/room.rpy:574
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_bedeeabc:

    # ermy_game "They looked like they wanted to tell me something, but all I could hear was that annoying buzz. Or maybe it sounded more like a distorted phone call… doesn’t matter though."
    ermy_game "他們看來想跟我說些什麼，可是我所聽到的隻有那種讓人火大的嗡嗡聲。或者，它可能更像是那個熟悉的電話鈴聲……無所謂了。"

# game/room.rpy:575
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_4091e76b:

    # ermy_game "I don’t think I’m supposed to be here."
    ermy_game "我不應該在這裡。"

# game/room.rpy:576
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_7df35926:

    # ermy_game "I spent enough time in this otherwise unremarkable room, spare for a very weird note on a whiteboard."
    ermy_game "我在這個平常的房間裡呆了很長時間，在白板上留了一個奇怪的便條。"

# game/room.rpy:577
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a42734e2:

    # ermy_game "To leave this room, you must tell me the answer."
    ermy_game "要離開這裡，你必須給我一個答案。"

# game/room.rpy:578
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_2d473ecc:

    # ermy_game "What does it mean? Who 'me'? What’s the question to begin with?"
    ermy_game "這是什麼意思？‘給我’是給誰？首先，要回答的到底是什麼問題？"

# game/room.rpy:579
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_993cdf82:

    # ermy_game "The only semblance of a hint came from a few more words below. Four in total: \"Love\", \"Hate\", \"Life\", \"Death\"."
    ermy_game "唯一的提示是下面寫的幾個詞。一共有四個：\"愛情\", \"仇恨\", \"人生\", \"死亡\"。"

# game/room.rpy:580
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_7594ef6b:

    # ermy_game "Well… so what of it?"
    ermy_game "所以……那又怎麼樣？"

# game/room.rpy:582
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ff49ed50:

    # e1 "All this makes no sense"
    e1 "所有這些都沒什麼意義。"

# game/room.rpy:584
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_c345e091:

    # s1 "I know, dear. What is the question, I wonder? That’s what my friend and I are trying to realize."
    s1 "我知道,親愛的。我想知道問題是什麼?這就是我和我的朋友想要了解的。"

# game/room.rpy:586
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0868d950:

    # "A young woman appears seemingly out of nowhere. Dressed in an overly tight nurse uniform, she carries a syringe filled with a strange, bright liquid."
    "一個年輕的女孩子不知從什麼地方冒了出來。身上穿著緊致的護士服，她拿著一支含有奇怪液體的注射器。"

# game/room.rpy:587
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_cb8159dd:

    # e1 "Who are you?"
    e1 "你是誰？"

# game/room.rpy:589
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_dcafaa9b:

    # s1 "My name is Sophie. Nice to meet you! As for my friend, he doesn’t talk much, so I’m afraid I can’t introduce him to you properly."
    s1 "我叫索菲。很高興認識你！至於我的朋友，他不愛說話，因此恐怕無法把你正式地介紹給他。"

# game/room.rpy:591
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_aa0ed32b:

    # e1 "Your friend?"
    e1 "你的朋友？"

# game/room.rpy:593
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_c8ec2342:

    # s1 "Yes, here, right in my hand. My precious friend who always knows the truth. Always but today it seems."
    s1 "對，這裡，就在我的手裡。我那了解真相的珍貴的朋友。今天之外，也一直都是。"

# game/room.rpy:595
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_679519ed:

    # "I thought back to my military training… The best way to deal with mentally unstable people is to take them seriously."
    "我回想了一下我的軍訓。對待精神狀態不穩定的人最好的方法就是讓他們認真起來。"

# game/room.rpy:596
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d0f3046b:

    # e1 "I guess it’s nice to have such a wise friend."
    e1 "我想有那麼睿智的朋友應該還不錯吧。"

# game/room.rpy:598
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_09b3c39d:

    # s1 "More like \"persistent\", I should say. It takes my friend quite some time to kick in but then there’s no stopping him, and you’re guaranteed to tell me everything I want."
    s1 "實際上，\"執著\"這個詞會更合適些。我的朋友雖然需要一點時間才能開始行動，可一旦開始后就沒有東西可以阻止他了。你保証會告訴我我想知道的一切。"

# game/room.rpy:602
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_31736c0e:

    # "She moves closer, and I can’t help but notice that the button on Sophie’s blouse is about to be ripped off by her… well…"
    "她走得更近了，我不由自主地注意到蘇菲上衣上的紐扣就要被她扯掉了……。"

# game/room.rpy:607
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b5889205:

    # s1 "Hey darling, care to have a taste? Who knows, maybe you’re just pretending, not willing to tell me the answer… Hey, I really want to get out of this place. I don’t think I’m supposed be here."
    s1 "誒，親愛的，想嘗一嘗嗎？誰知道，你也許假裝不願意告訴我答案……嘿，我真想離開這兒了。我不覺得我應該在這裡。"

# game/room.rpy:615
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e99bbab8:

    # m1 "Stay away, she’s clearly out of her mind."
    m1 "離她遠遠的， 她分明是瘋了。"

# game/room.rpy:617
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_4faeb802:

    # "This room gets more crowded, now that a second girl, wrapped up in a latex costume serving presumably no other purpose rather than an aesthetic one, shows up in front of me."
    "第二個女孩兒進來后站在我前面時，房間就此刻變得更加擁擠。她穿著一套好像隻為審美服務的乳膠衣服。"

# game/room.rpy:619
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f43514bc:

    # s1 "I’m much saner than you… Megan, right? At least I’m not making up a ridiculous explanation of what bound us all together here like you do."
    s1 "我比你正常多了……梅根，對吧？我至少不會為我們被限制在這裡想出可笑的解釋。"

# game/room.rpy:623
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_c8a8866f:

    # m1 "It’s not ridiculous, it’s true. I come from an era far more advanced than yours, I know things you can’t even imagine."
    m1 "它們並不可笑的，它們都是真實的。和你的時代相比我所處的時代發達多了，所以我知道的事情你甚至不能想象。"

# game/room.rpy:627
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_58bc8214:

    # s1 "See? That’s what I’m talking about. Megan think she’s from the future."
    s1 "理解了嗎？這就是我想說的。梅根覺得她來自未來。"

# game/room.rpy:631
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a148509d:

    # m1 "Still don’t believe me? Fine. What’s your last memory before you got here? I’m asking you as well, by the way. What’s your name?"
    m1 "還是不相信我嗎?好吧。到這兒之前，你的最后的記憶是什麼？順便問你，你叫什麼名字？"

# game/room.rpy:633
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_74f4a0d0:

    # e1 "Hermes."
    e1 "赫耳墨斯。"

# game/room.rpy:635
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_54bce0ef:

    # m1 "So, Hermes, do you remember anything?"
    m1 "所以，赫耳墨斯，你記得起來任何事情嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:637
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_6652deee:

    # e1 "I heard the phone ringing somewhere very close to where I was."
    e1 "我記得聽到離我很近的電話聲響。"

# game/room.rpy:638
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_67b6813c:

    # "The second I say that the phone starts ringing again. Ring-ring… ring-ring… like those machines in old detective phones."
    "我說這句話的時候，電話一下子就開始響了。鈴鈴……鈴鈴……似乎就像那些老式警用電話裡的鈴聲一樣 。"

# game/room.rpy:639
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_15038066:

    # "The sound becomes more and more loud. My head hurts! Someone should stop it. Pick up the phone, please…"
    "聲音越來越大。我的頭疼欲裂！別讓它響了，接電話，拜托……"

# game/room.rpy:641
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_24caa050:

    # m1 "What did you say?"
    m1 "你剛說什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:643
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_36b25b49:

    # e1 "Can you hear it?"
    e1 "能聽到嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:645
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ea6891f3:

    # m1 "Hear what?"
    m1 "聽到什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:647
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_43daaf35:

    # e1 "That phone ringing over and over again… Jeez, it really gets on my nerves."
    e1 "電話一直響……天哪，那聲音真叫我心煩。"

# game/room.rpy:649
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_abd216de:

    # m1 "My, this room must be a hangout spot for weirdos. And I thought it couldn’t be worse than when our spaceship was invaded by those creatures…"
    m1 "天哪，這個房間一定是怪人聚集的地方。我想沒有比我們的太空船被那些生物入侵更壞的事了。"

# game/room.rpy:652
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_adf1fed7:

    # s1 "Please don’t mention this word again, Megan."
    s1 "請你別再說這個詞，梅根。"

# game/room.rpy:656
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_80ad3d76:

    # m1 "What are you talking about?"
    m1 "你在說什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:660
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_c226c8fb:

    # s1 "Hang, you said… what a painful word. I was doing my daily routine, helping people to open up and talk… the guy we had back then, he just couldn’t relax, he was so nervous!"
    s1 "等一下，你說……哎呀，那麼令人痛苦的詞。我做我的日常工作來幫助人們敞開心扉暢所欲言……那個家伙，他一直很緊張不能放鬆下來！"

# game/room.rpy:661
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a9f9cb3e:

    # s1 "\"You won’t get a single word out of me!\" he shouted, rolling eyes like a madman. So silly of him! Then I heard the footsteps…"
    s1 "\"你別想從我嘴裡得到一個字！\"他喊著，愚蠢地像瘋子一樣轉著他的眼睛。那一刻我聽到了腳步的聲音……"

# game/room.rpy:662
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_14c1ee5f:

    # s1 "Bam! They ran out the door and barged in. \"Hey girl, nothing personal, but we don’t like to see our friend suffer. That’s a nice rope you tied him with, by the way. Why don’t we really put it to use?\""
    s1 "嘭的一下！他們從門口跑進來。\"嘿美女，拋開私人恩怨，可是我們不喜歡看到朋友受罪。對了，你把他綁住的那條繩子挺不錯啊。我們為什麼不好好的利用一下它呢？"

# game/room.rpy:664
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b761caf6:

    # "Sophie shivers and stops talking."
    "索菲渾身顫抖地閉嘴了。"

# game/room.rpy:666
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b319f4e8:

    # m1 "Hm… I think I just realized that, although we came from different eras, we share one thing in common."
    m1 "嗯……我覺得我才意識到，雖然咱們是來自不同的時代，我們有一個共同的東西"

# game/room.rpy:670
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e555018e:

    # n1 "Yes, yes! We’re all dead nyaw! Naomi knows what she’s talking about!"
    n1 "對對！咱們都死了，喵！娜奧米知道她在說什麼！"

# game/room.rpy:672
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_475e70c9:

    # "A cute girl, dressed in a maid outfit, joins the conversation. Where was she hiding? Weird… By the way, she holds a plushie in one hand."
    "一個穿著一套女仆服的漂亮女孩兒加入對話。她之前在哪兒？奇怪……她手裡拿著一個毛絨玩具。"

# game/room.rpy:674
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_50d5f946:

    # n1 "What,can’t you see it? You can, can’t you? You just don’t want to admit it… Ease up – death is the best answer-nya!"
    n1 "什麼，你不能理解嗎？應該能理解的啊？隻是不願意承認吧……放鬆！死亡就是最好的答案喵！"

# game/room.rpy:677
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0082ea6d:

    # m1 "This little brat… She keeps spouting nonsense."
    m1 "這小壞蛋……她總是胡言亂語。"

# game/room.rpy:680
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_36548f26:

    # n1 "Why, I’m just trying to play this game! Unlike you, I realized these are all answers and death is the best one of them all!"
    n1 "才不是！我隻是想試著玩這個游戲！我可不像你，我早已經發現這些就是所有的答案，並且其中最好的就是死亡！"

# game/room.rpy:682
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f3906536:

    # "Ring-ring…"
    "鈴鈴……"

# game/room.rpy:684
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d5ff5190:

    # m1 "Death is certainly not an answer to anything, but, you know, if it helps us to get out of this place, I’m fine with it. I really need to head back home."
    m1 "死亡肯定不是答案，可是你知道 如果你能幫我們離開這裡的話，我都無所謂。我真的想回家。"

# game/room.rpy:687
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f8d8e8e8:

    # n1 "No one likes the dead coming back, I’m afraid~"
    n1 "恐怕沒人喜歡死人回去。"

# game/room.rpy:690
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_10edb993:

    # m1 "I’m not dead!"
    m1 "我才沒死！"

# game/room.rpy:693
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a924797c:

    # s1 "I agree with Naomi… maybe death is the ultimate answer to everything. At the very least, it has the ultimate degree of certainty."
    s1 "我同意娜奧米的想法……也許死亡是一切的最終答案。至少，它具有最終的確定性。"
# game/room.rpy:696
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_6be526f0:

    # m1 "What?"
    m1 "什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:699
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5da7b0a8:

    # s1 "Well, how do you know whether or not you actually live? What qualifies you as a living person?"
    s1 "我是說，你怎麼知道你是否真的活著，什麼使你有資格成為有生命的人？"

# game/room.rpy:702
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_2cf8bddc:

    # m1 "Ridiculous. Don’t be silly. My heartbeat, for instance."
    m1 "荒唐！別犯傻了。我的心跳就可以証明。"

# game/room.rpy:705
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_20ce8586:

    # s1 "Then you compare yourself to an animal."
    s1 "那樣，你就是把自己等同於動物。"

# game/room.rpy:708
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_00094163:

    # m1 "You’re getting on my nerves."
    m1 "真讓我火大。"

# game/room.rpy:711
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5c42052a:

    # s1 "Hey, I’m just trying to say that, compared to the lives of some people, you’re just occupying space. On the other hand, when you die, you’re one hundred percent dead. Everyone is equal 6 feet underground. No one can challenge this fact."
    s1 "誒誒，我的意思是 和有些人的生命比起來，你活的毫無意義。不過，你一旦死了，就百分之百死了。在死亡中，人人都平等。這個毋庸置疑。"

# game/room.rpy:714
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5bfadf91:

    # m1 "Spoken like a true genius."
    m1 "你以為自己是天才嗎。"

# game/room.rpy:717
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_4fa02821:

    # s1 "I know, right? I’m an underappreciated asset."
    s1 "我是啊，對嗎？不要低估我的能力。"

# game/room.rpy:720
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_46461007:

    # m1 "Where are you from, again?"
    m1 "我再問一次你來自哪裡？"

# game/room.rpy:723
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_84a541f5:

    # s1 "The present time."
    s1 "此刻這裡。"

# game/room.rpy:726
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_3c658ae3:

    # n1 "Death is the answer simply because eternal life is much worse."
    n1 "死亡是答案僅僅是因為它比永生好多了。"

# game/room.rpy:728
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d077672c:

    # e1 "Say what?"
    e1 "什麼意思？"

# game/room.rpy:730
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_2e89f4f4:

    # n1 "I think I still have my magic powers to show you. Kitty cat, kitty cat! Make me happy, make them sad!"
    n1 "我覺得我應該用我的魔力展示給你看。小貓，小貓！讓我開心，讓他們難過！"
# game/room.rpy:732
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_7a29c0fd:

    # "I’m quite sure she’s referring to that plushie."
    "我很確定她指的是那個毛絨玩具。"

# game/room.rpy:734
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_70808d71:

    # e1 "Um, so what’s going to happen now?"
    e1 "嗯，現在會發生什麼事情？"

# game/room.rpy:736
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9dacbfe4:

    # n1 "Eternity!"
    n1 "永恆！"

# game/room.rpy:738
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_1339ec42:

    # e1 "What do you mean?"
    e1 "什麼意思？"

# game/room.rpy:740
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_136d5ffa:

    # n1 "Time will go, but we won’t follow!"
    n1 "時間會過去，但我們不會跟隨！"

# game/room.rpy:742
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0ae46a18:

    # "And she was right."
    "原來，她是對的。"

# game/room.rpy:776
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_1db227a2:

    # s1 "What day is it today?"
    s1 "今天是周幾？"

# game/room.rpy:779
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_60e4a148:

    # n1 "Friday-nya!"
    n1 "周五喵！"

# game/room.rpy:782
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9e96918a:

    # m1 "Jeez, how would you know? Thanks for your trick, time lost its meaning."
    m1 "天哪，你怎麼知道的呀？感謝你的把戲，現在時間失去意義了。"

# game/room.rpy:785
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_976d7936:

    # n1 "Therefore, it might as well always be Friday?"
    n1 "所以，也許總是周五？"

# game/room.rpy:788
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d1fc1a68:

    # m1 "It’s been what… days, months, years?"
    m1 "已經過了好幾……天、月還是年？"

# game/room.rpy:791
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_391c93e5:

    # s1 "Hey Naomi, can you revert your spell?"
    s1 "嗨，娜奧米，你能把你的魔咒取消嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:794
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b80c981a:

    # n1 "Tee-hee… if you all admit death is the answer, maybe I could!"
    n1 "嘻嘻……要是你們願意承認死亡是答案，我也許可以考慮！"

# game/room.rpy:797
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b8404223:

    # s1 "Okay, I admit it."
    s1 "好吧，我承認。"

# game/room.rpy:800
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e55242c7:

    # m1 "No way I’m going to fall for this trick. You want to stay here forever? Fine, let’s talk. Little by little, the future will come, and that’s exactly where I’m from."
    m1 "我不會上你的當！你們想永遠都在這兒嗎？沒問題，讓我們聊一下。未來一定會慢慢到來，而那正是我來的地方。"

# game/room.rpy:803
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8cdca407:

    # n1 "Okay! Let’s talk about cats."
    n1 "好吧！讓我們談談小貓。"

# game/room.rpy:804
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_11f14ddd:

    # "So we did."
    "我們就談了小貓。"

# game/room.rpy:808
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_da68c765:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about food."
    n1 "讓我們談談吃的。"

# game/room.rpy:812
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_87a14ef5:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about fun."
    n1 "讓我們談談好玩的。"

# game/room.rpy:816
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9cbe8c04:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about films."
    n1 "讓我們談談電影。"

# game/room.rpy:820
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5a8cc362:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about fiction."
    n1 "讓我們談談小說。"

# game/room.rpy:824
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b7d8ac00:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about friends."
    n1 "讓我們談談朋友。"

# game/room.rpy:828
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_16f0aa98:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about freedom."
    n1 "讓我們談談自由。"

# game/room.rpy:832
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_48c514a9:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about feelings."
    n1 "讓我們談談感情。"

# game/room.rpy:836
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_15420724:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about foals."
    n1 "讓我們談談小馬駒。"

# game/room.rpy:840
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_15658208:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about foxes."
    n1 "讓我們談談狐狸。"

# game/room.rpy:844
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8805db41:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about forests."
    n1 "讓我們談談森林。"

# game/room.rpy:848
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_39de2463:

    # n1 "Let’s talk about fonts."
    n1 "讓我們談談字體。"

# game/room.rpy:853
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d5add85d:

    # m1 "Stop it! I can’t take it anymore!"
    m1 "夠了！我受不了了！"

# game/room.rpy:855
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0f435484:

    # m1 "Fine, maybe death is the answer. Whatever…"
    m1 "好的，死亡是答案。算了……"

# game/room.rpy:857
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5014debd:

    # "I too agreed with that. However, nothing happened."
    "我也同意，但是，什麼都沒發生。"

# game/room.rpy:858
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a5497450:

    # e1 "Uh, what’s next? What should we do?"
    e1 "嗯……下一步是什麼？ 我們應該做什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:860
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_3d74f157:

    # s1 "I think we should be more proactive, now that we all agree on our answer. See this purple liquid? It’s the last resort liquid, so to speak. Let me help you, friends…"
    s1 "我覺得一旦咱們都同意了，就該更加積極主動。大家能看到這個紫色的液體了嗎？這是最后一個了。讓我幫你們一下，朋友們……"

# game/room.rpy:861
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_55b44aa5:

    # "She moves so swiftly. It doesn’t even hurt… My vision starts to become blurry."
    "她迅速行動起來。還沒感到疼痛，我的眼前就變得模糊起來。"

# game/room.rpy:863
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a75c52f6:

    # "Ring-ring. The phone rings again, but this time I manage to answer it, somehow."
    "叮鈴鈴。電話再次響起，但是這次我設法接起電話。"

# game/room.rpy:864
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_84e76fe8:

    # "The guy on the other end of the line tells me that if I die, I’ll stay in this room forever. Uhm… why haven’t I thought about it before?"
    "電話那頭的家伙跟我說要是我死亡，就會永遠留在這個房間裡。哼……我怎麼之前沒想到呢？"

# game/room.rpy:865
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5833a61e:

    # "I’m afraid it’s too late now."
    "恐怕現在已經太晚了。"

# game/room.rpy:867
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_6cafbc94:

    # "\"Love\""
    "\"愛情\""

# game/room.rpy:868
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d2faa229:

    # e1 "Love? What is love?"
    e1 "愛情？愛情是什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:870
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_4d464fd2:

    # n1 "Baby don’t hurt me… oh, pardon me! Hi! What would your order be?"
    n1 "寶貝別傷到我……哦，對不起！嗨！您要點什麼？"
# game/room.rpy:871
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_95474de9:

    # e1 "Naomi? You’re… alive?"
    e1 "娜奧米？你……活著嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:873
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_59914448:

    # n1 "Yes, why? However, I woke up in this room today. You know, that milk tea I had yesterday… it tasted so weird. Anyway, although it’s not my tavern anymore , I certainly have a customer."
    n1 "當然，怎麼了？可是，我今天在這個房間醒來了。你知道，昨天的那杯奶茶……味道好奇怪。反正，雖然這裡不是我的酒館，但我肯定會有個客人。"

# game/room.rpy:874
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_84a1e791:

    # e1 "What can I order?"
    e1 "我可以點什麼菜？"

# game/room.rpy:876
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e20e6c41:

    # n1 "Nothing, I’m afraid. We’re short on everything. But I can make you company! I’m a good maid, after all."
    n1 "恐怕什麼都不可以。我們什麼都沒有。但是，我可以陪你！畢竟我是個女仆。"

# game/room.rpy:877
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b1a80b2d:

    # e1 "Did you see this strange whiteboard?"
    e1 "你有看到那個奇怪的白板嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:879
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_c2949f2c:

    # n1 "Sure I did! What do you think the answer is-nya?"
    n1 "當然！你覺得答案是什麼喵？"

# game/room.rpy:880
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5b3ee10e:

    # e1 "Love."
    e1 "愛情。"

# game/room.rpy:882
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_51562a0a:

    # n1 "How romantic of you! Sadly, I know nothing of it. I’m not allowed to get into an affair with a customer, even with one as handsome as you. However… let my magic do the work and say whether or not you’re right-nya! Kitty cat, kitty cat, make me happy, make them sad!"
    n1 "你真浪漫！很可惜我對愛情不了解。我不被允許和客人交往，即使客人像你這麼帥。不過……讓我使用我的魔力確認你是對的還是錯的喵！小貓小貓!讓我開心讓他們難過！"

# game/room.rpy:883
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_6f62cd52:

    # "Two other girls appear right in front of my eyes."
    "兩個其他的女孩子突然出現就在我眼前。"

# game/room.rpy:887
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8551e79d:

    # n1 "Tell me, what is love?"
    n1 "告訴我，愛情是什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:890
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_3ffa9ff9:

    # m1 "Love is reducible to the absurd act of chemicals. Therefore, there is no intrinsic value in this material universe."
    m1 "愛情可以說是一種荒謬的化學反應。因此，它在這個物質世界沒什麼固有價值。"

# game/room.rpy:893
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_31306ef3:

    # s1 "Hypocrite that you are, for you trust the chemicals in your brain to tell you they are chemicals. All knowledge is ultimately based on that which we cannot prove. Will you fight? Or will you perish like a dog?"
    s1 "你好虛偽，因為你相信你腦子裡的化學物質跟你說它就是化學物質。所有的知識都建立在我們無法証明的基礎上。你要反抗嗎？還是要像個狗一樣死掉呢？"

# game/room.rpy:896
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_7a418a0b:

    # n1 "Sorry, they’re a bit broken. Let me fix it-nya!"
    n1 "對不起，她們壞了一點點。我來修一下喵！"

# game/room.rpy:904
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8551e79d_1:

    # n1 "Tell me, what is love?"
    n1 "告訴我，愛情是什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:905
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_6974623a:

    # "Silence was her answer."
    "沉默是她的答案。"

# game/room.rpy:907
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ba59fce4:

    # n1 "Oh my, oh my, still no good. Well, let me try this little trick! In a second, they’re going to fall for you, Hermes!"
    n1 "天哪，還不行。讓我試一下這個小把戲！一瞬間她們就會愛上你了，赫耳墨斯！"

# game/room.rpy:909
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_3d645029:

    # "She spanks me with her plushie."
    "她用她的玩具打我的屁股。"

# game/room.rpy:911
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_abcbdcc3:

    # "I notice Sophie and Megan staring at me."
    "我發現索菲和梅根盯著我看。"

# game/room.rpy:913
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_1a883a9b:

    # m1 "Um, Hermes?"
    m1 "嗯……赫耳墨斯？"

# game/room.rpy:914
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e728d812:

    # e1 "Yes?"
    e1 "嗯？"

# game/room.rpy:916
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_da584911:

    # m1 "I… I love you."
    m1 "我……我愛你。"

# game/room.rpy:917
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_190fa817:

    # e1 "Why?"
    e1 "為什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:919
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e0b9e159:

    # m1 "Should I have a reason?"
    m1 "還要原因嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:920
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ca4c5a22:

    # e1 "No, but I’m curious."
    e1 "不要，就是好奇。"

# game/room.rpy:922
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_cd0d4e7a:

    # m1 "Just because you’re here."
    m1 "隻是因為你在這兒。"

# game/room.rpy:923
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9a0c13f9:

    # e1 "I’ve been here before."
    e1 "我以前來過啊。"

# game/room.rpy:925
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d1545791:

    # m1 "Really? Well, people change, don’t they?"
    m1 "真的嗎？哼……人們總是在改變，對吧？"

# game/room.rpy:928
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5188dce6:

    # s1 "He’s mine! He will be my darling. Only you and I forever more, Hermes."
    s1 "他是我的！他要當我親愛的。隻有你和我，永遠在一起，赫耳墨斯。"

# game/room.rpy:929
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ce95f0e8:

    # e1 "Hey, we’re kind of stuck here together."
    e1 "嗨，我們一起陷在這裡了。"

# game/room.rpy:932
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_63d0fcdd:

    # n1 "But if you could leave… which one of them would you choose to go with you-nya?"
    n1 "但是，要是你能離開……想她們其中哪個跟你一起走呢喵？"

# game/room.rpy:936
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5db9a200:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "你行為好奇怪。這些名字我都不認識。"

# game/room.rpy:939
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5db9a200_1:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "你行為好奇怪。這些名字我都不認識。"

# game/room.rpy:942
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5db9a200_2:

    # n1 "You’re being weird. I don’t recognize any of these names."
    n1 "你行為好奇怪。這些名字我都不認識。"

# game/room.rpy:945
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b7057560:

    # m1 "It hurts me that you’d think of other girls during a moment like this."
    m1 "你這種時刻還會想著其他的女孩子真讓我感到傷心。"

# game/room.rpy:948
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_94d97829:

    # s1 "Yeah, how could you? It’s so selfish… from another side, love is the most selfish feeling anyway."
    s1 "對吧，你怎麼能這麼做？那麼自私……可是，從另一個角度看，愛情是世界上最自私的感情。"

# game/room.rpy:950
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_2f5d78a1:

    # e1 "What?"
    e1 "什麼意思？"

# game/room.rpy:952
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d4d70ff8:

    # s1 "Selfish, of course, if it’s not eternal… and what is eternal love? Eternal love means you should stay together until the very end. Till death do us part!"
    s1 "當然如果愛情不是永恆的，那就是自私的……永恆的愛情是什麼？永恆的愛情意味著你們一直都要在一起。直至死亡將你們分開！"

# game/room.rpy:954
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_98b90bd4:

    # s1 "Now, I’m sure that after some time you’re definitely going to choose me over anyone else. The question is, how can I be sure that your feeling lasts forever?"
    s1 "現在呢，我完全確定過一會你一定會選擇我，可是問題是我怎麼來保証你的愛情會始終如一？"

# game/room.rpy:957
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_114a833d:

    # m1 "What are you talking about? Stop babbling nonsense."
    m1 "你在說什麼？別胡說了。"

# game/room.rpy:960
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_98e9d238:

    # s1 "Trust me, my words make perfect sense. Here, let my friend explain this to you."
    s1 "相信我，我說的十分有道理。我的朋友來給你解釋。"

# game/room.rpy:965
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_c62123ff:

    # "She does a few quick swings, and shortly after that we’re the only ones standing in the room."
   "她快速走了幾步，不久之后，我們是唯一站在房間裡的人。"

# game/room.rpy:966
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_75b83749:

    # e1 "W-what have you done? How could you?"
    e1 "你做了什麼？你怎麼能？"

# game/room.rpy:968
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_011582e6:

    # s1 "Same as you, I’m just being selfish. All fair and square! Fair… you know what? Love is not the answer. Love is not fair."
    s1 "和你一樣，我就是自私的。公平而公正！公正……你知道麼?愛情不是答案。愛情並不公正。"

# game/room.rpy:970
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_4de88049:

    # "I feel cold sweat dripping down my back. Sophie’s clearly bonkers, and I need to calm her down somehow."
    "我感覺到背后一陣冷汗。索菲顯然是瘋子，我需要讓她平靜下來。"

# game/room.rpy:971
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_fecabd29:

    # e1 "Not fair? But why? I always thought love is one of the best feelings in the world."
    e1 "不公正嗎？這為什麼？我一直都覺得愛情是世界上最好的感情之一。"

# game/room.rpy:973
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f3bb75fb:

    # s1 "I never said it’s bad, I said it’s not fair. Love should be mutual, but it never works that way."
    s1 "我沒說它不好，而是說它不公正。愛情該是相互的，可它從來不這樣。"

# game/room.rpy:975
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_61d98b07:

    # s1 "Remember, Hermes, between two people involved, one loves while the other allows himself or herself to be loved. How is this fair?"
    s1 "要記得，赫耳墨斯，兩個人裡其中一個人是愛對方的，而另一個就讓自己被愛著。這怎麼公平呢？"

# game/room.rpy:977
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a8cb72eb:

    # e1 "I don’t believe you."
    e1 "我不相信你。"

# game/room.rpy:979
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b3c2b8c9:

    # s1 "Oh, and love is also very selfish, remember? Even more selfish than you and me."
    s1 "再說，愛情總是很自私，還記得嗎？比我和你還自私。"

# game/room.rpy:981
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_dc7a5c78:

    # e1 "What about love you have for your parents?"
    e1"你對父母的愛呢？"

# game/room.rpy:983
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ed3c846a:

    # s1 "It all goes down the same street. Every time you buy them something, you feel like a good kid. In a way, you buy it for yourself, Hermes... Now, what I’m going to do is to have you all for myself."
    s1 "一樣的。你每次給他們買東西，都會覺得自己是好孩子。在一定程度上，你是為了自己而買那些東西，赫耳墨斯。現在，我要做的就是讓大家珍惜自己。"

# game/room.rpy:984
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8af92fc8:

    # "Swing! The needle bites me like a snake. My legs start to tremble."
    "針就像蛇一樣咬住我。我的腿開始發抖。"

# game/room.rpy:986
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_476cf9b6:

    # s1 "It feels so… satisfying!"
    s1 "感覺那麼……令人滿意。"

# game/room.rpy:988
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ae199ff2:

    # "Sophie’s face is the last thing to flash in my mind before darkness covers everything around me."
    "黑暗席卷我之前，索菲的臉是我最后看到的影像。"

# game/room.rpy:994
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_80661c14:

    # "I’m back from the dead, it seems. Even more, the usual crowd’s here, as if nothing happened at all. The phone starts ringing again."
    "看來我復活了。這幾個人也都在，似乎什麼都沒發生。電話又響起來了。"

# game/room.rpy:995
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e0285bd8:

    # "I don’t think I can get rid of that pain in my head, so I badly need to concentrate on something else… maybe small talk can help."
    "我頭疼不止，所以我非常需要轉移注意力……聊天也許能有幫助。"

# game/room.rpy:996
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_598cb488:

    # e1 "Hey, do you guys remember what just happened?"
    e1 "嗨，大家，你們記得剛剛發生什麼事情了麼？"

# game/room.rpy:998
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_3bad760e:

    # m1 "Um, nothing yet? We have to find the answer, and…"
    m1 "嗯，目前沒什麼？我們得想出對的答案，然后……"

# game/room.rpy:1001
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0bf62620:

    # n1 "And I’m sure the answer is one of these words-nya!"
    n1 "我確定答案是這些詞語其中之一喵！"

# game/room.rpy:1003
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_02f3e9ea:

    # "You’re kidding me. Have they entirely forgotten about what happened before?"
    "你一定是在開玩笑。她們難道把所有之前發生的事情都忘了嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:1005
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_fba2a399:

    # s1 "Hm… which word would it be?"
    s1 "哼……你想的是哪一個詞？"

# game/room.rpy:1008
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_630b973a:

    # n1 "Easy… Hate! Hate is the answer!"
    n1 "很簡單……仇恨！答案肯定是仇恨！"

# game/room.rpy:1011
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_15b26fae:

    # s1 "Why do you think so?"
    s1 "你為什麼這麼想？"

# game/room.rpy:1014
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9b3d3d1b:

    # n1 "Well, I hate you all, so this word is definitely a suitable answer for me. "
    n1 "你看 我恨你們所有人，因此對我來說，這個答案是最合適的。"

# game/room.rpy:1017
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_1adc9e55:

    # m1 "For you, yes, for me, no."
    m1 "對你來說是，對我不是。"

# game/room.rpy:1020
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0aee5c79:

    # n1 "But why would I care about you-nya?"
    n1 "可是我為什麼要在意你們呢喵？"

# game/room.rpy:1023
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_17c8dc61:

    # s1 "I wonder what’s your reason for hating us that much."
    s1 "我也想知道，你那麼恨我們的原因是什麼。"

# game/room.rpy:1026
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_32f53bf8:

    # n1 "It’s simple, you know-nya… I hate you because you leave me no hope."
    n1 "很簡答 你知道喵……因為你們不給我希望，所以我恨你們。"

# game/room.rpy:1029
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e6d2010d:

    # s1 "Why, I wonder?"
    s1 "為什麼，我想知道？"

# game/room.rpy:1032
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_32411d59:

    # n1 "If you’re right and I came from the past, then I see my future in the two of you. What can I say? This future looks pathetic…"
    n1 "如果你是對的，我來自過去，那麼我會在你們兩個中看到我的未來。我還能說什麼？這種未來看起來很可悲……"

# game/room.rpy:1035
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_83e47828:

    # m1 "But you don’t know us at all."
    m1 "可是你根本不理解我們。"

# game/room.rpy:1038
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f8f12659:

    # n1 "Even five minutes is enough. I despise you."
    n1 "五分鐘就夠了。我鄙視你們。"

# game/room.rpy:1040
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8e2bb17a:

    # "Her annoyance doesn’t seem to be justified at the very slightest, but I’m not surprised, as it fits perfectly with the weird ambiance of that place."
    "她的生氣看來一點道理也沒有，可我並不吃驚。這正好符合這個地方古怪的氣氛。"

# game/room.rpy:1042
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b0648637:

    # s1 "I don’t think hate is the answer because it’s too easy to hate something."
    s1 "我覺得仇恨是答案的可能性不大，因為恨某個東西總是太容易了。"

# game/room.rpy:1044
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f877b003:

    # e1 "And who said the answer should be complicated?"
    e1 "誰說答案一定要復雜呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1046
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_decd0964:

    # s1 "What do you hate, Hermes?"
    s1 "你最恨什麼，赫耳墨斯？"

# game/room.rpy:1048
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_852a002a:

    # e1 "Other people."
    e1 "別人。"

# game/room.rpy:1050
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_552b1ac7:

    # s1 "Including me?"
    s1 "包括我嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:1052
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d3978f51:

    # e1 "We just met, but I’m sure I’m capable of developing a whole nanoangstrom of hate directed towards you."
    e1 "我們剛剛見面，可是我確定有一天會很恨你。"

# game/room.rpy:1054
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d1423817:

    # s1 "Why?"
    s1 "為什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:1057
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b93fe669:

    # m1 "Yeah, why?"
    m1 "對啊，為什麼呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1059
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d256d946:

    # e1 "Because you make me feel like I’m not supposed to be here."
    e1 "因為你讓我感到我不應該在這裡。"

# game/room.rpy:1061
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ae425021:

    # m1 "What would’ve changed had we not existed at all?"
    m1 "如果我們根本不存在會有什麼改變 ？"

# game/room.rpy:1064
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e6ce7e7b:

    # n1 "Then he couldn’t compare. If he had no other place to be, his thought would become invalid. I agree with you, Hermes. If I hadn’t seen the future right before my eyes, I’d have been fine with everything."
    n1 "那他就無從比較。如果他沒有其他地方可以去，他的想法就沒有意義。我同意你的看法，赫耳墨斯。要是我沒有親眼看到未來，我會覺得怎樣都可以。"

# game/room.rpy:1067
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_3d61b9c5:

    # s1 "You guys don’t even know about the right reason to hate everyone around you. I mean… they exist. They smell, they take space, they’re loud and annoying. That’s why I always stay in my lab, so I could have some personal space. But even there, when I visit the bathroom, I look in the mirror and realize I’m no different."
    s1 "你們甚至找不到恨周圍每個人的正當理由。我是說……他們存在、他們呼吸、佔用空間、他們吵到讓人心煩。這就是為什麼我一直待在實驗室裡的原因，這裡我可以有一些私人空間。但是即使在這兒，每當我去洗手間時，我看著鏡子裡的自己意識到自己沒有什麼不同。"# game/room.rpy:1069
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f6bf548f:

    # e1 "What about you, Megan?"
    e1 "你呢，梅根？"

# game/room.rpy:1071
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_7fd3821b:

    # m1 "I don’t know. In the future, our personalities are removed as they serve little to no purpose. We don’t live, we function. I still have some emotions but hate is too strong, it’s off limits."
    m1 "我不知道。將來我們的個性都將被刪除，因為它們幾乎沒有用處。我們不是活著，是指單純地發揮作用。我仍然會有些情緒，但是仇恨感太強烈了，這是不可以的。"

# game/room.rpy:1078
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_550e2853:

    # n1 "Hermes! Hi-nya! Finally, it’s only me and you here!"
    n1 "赫耳墨斯！嗨喵！終於隻剩咱們兩個人了！"

# game/room.rpy:1080
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f887d2da:

    # e1 "Where has everyone else gone?"
    e1 "其他人去哪兒了？"

# game/room.rpy:1082
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_bfd62e5b:

    # n1 "What makes you think they’ve ever been here to begin with?"
    n1 "是什麼讓你認為他們曾經來過這裡？"

# game/room.rpy:1084
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_97e6d0a1:

    # n1 "Anyway… I’m here to support you-nya! Trust me, hate is not the answer! Life, yes, life is!"
    n1 "反正……我是支持你的喵！相信我，仇恨不是答案！生活才是！"

# game/room.rpy:1086
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_432f24e4:

    # n1 "I want you to know that you’re supposed to be here with me. Stay with me forever, Hermes."
    n1 "我想讓你知道你應該和我一起在這裡。永遠和我在一起吧，赫耳墨斯。"

# game/room.rpy:1087
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_2c13b61e:

    # e1 "Why are you so sure about it?"
    e1 "你怎麼那麼確定？"

# game/room.rpy:1089
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0f6fd17d:

    # n1 "Because I don’t think this place was supposed to exist in the first place. It feels made up. Therefore, you fit in perfectly. Think of it as a new life for both of us."
    n1 "因為我覺得這個地方不應該存在。它是虛構的。你卻正好適合在這裡。我們可以在這裡開始我們兩個的新生活。"

# game/room.rpy:1090
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_fe6e732f:

    # e1 "Life… you think life is the answer?"
    e1 "生活……你認為生活是答案嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:1092
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_577273e1:

    # n1 "Yes, because I want to spend my life with you."
    n1 "是的，因為我想與你共度此生。"

# game/room.rpy:1093
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_57d2f7bf:

    # e1 "What… what are we going to do?"
    e1 "咱……咱們要做什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:1095
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_684cb5b8:

    # n1 "Everything but one thing… we’ll never walk alone. And… you know, I’m a maid. I can always serve you a cup of tea when you need it. Trust me, having a friend like this is what matters the most."
    n1 "除了一件事之外都可以……咱們永遠不會孤獨。還有……你知道 我是女仆。要是你需要，我總能給你泡一杯茶。相信我，有這種朋友才是最重要的。"

# game/room.rpy:1096
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e8238865:

    # e1 "Thanks, Naomi… I-I don’t even know what to say."
    e1 "謝謝娜奧米……我——我甚至不知道說什麼。"

# game/room.rpy:1098
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_072f1189:

    # s1 "It’s because you actually want to spend your whole life with me instead, you know."
    s1 "這也許是因為你確實想與我共度此生，而不是她？"

# game/room.rpy:1099
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8faeaea5:

    # e1 "Hey, where did Naomi go?"
    e1 "誒，娜奧米又去哪兒呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1101
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_791c8d49:

    # s1 "It doesn’t matter. It’s just you and I here now, Hermes. You and I."
    s1 "這不重要。現在隻有你和我兩個人了，赫耳墨斯。你和我。"

# game/room.rpy:1102
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_14657251:

    # e1 "What are we going to do?"
    e1 "咱們要做什麼呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1104
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5e6d7832:

    # s1 "We’re going to have some fun, you know. Admit it, that’s what you really want. Everything else is just a façade to mask your desire."
    s1 "我們會玩得很開心的 。承認吧，這就是你真正想要的。其他的一切隻是掩飾你這個欲望的面具。"

# game/room.rpy:1105
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a7246076:

    # e1 "T-that’s not true…"
    e1 "才——才不是……"

# game/room.rpy:1107
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0dba7c36:

    # s1 "Well, do you want my friend to ask you this question again? He’ll get an honest answer out of you."
    s1 "哼……你想我的朋友再次問你這個問題嗎？他肯定會從你那裡得到誠實的答案。"

# game/room.rpy:1108
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_dd9803ce:

    # e1 "T-there’s no need for that…"
    e1 "沒——沒有必要……"

# game/room.rpy:1110
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e31fba8a:

    # s1 "See? Now you’re being frank. Don’t worry, it’s okay. Think of yourself as a part of a hunter-gatherer world, it will make your life a whole lot easier. It’s just you, the things you own and the things you want to own."
    s1 "看到了吧。現在你很坦白。不用擔心，一切都好。你可以試想自己是世界的一部分，這樣你的生活會變得輕鬆多了。生活中隻有你自己，你擁有的東西和你想要擁有的東西。"

# game/room.rpy:1111
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f6c62981:

    # e1 "But I don’t want to think of you as a thing."
    e1 "可是我不想把你看做一個東西。"

# game/room.rpy:1113
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8c9c6948:

    # s1 "Well then, someone else would, my dear, and you’d be surprised about the choice I make."
    s1 "好吧，其他人會的，親愛的，你會對我的選擇感到驚訝。"
# game/room.rpy:1114
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_cedbf49f:

    # e1 "Life is not as primitive as you portray it."
    e1 "生活不像你描繪的那麼原始 。"

# game/room.rpy:1116
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_35f42b63:

    # s1 "Life works the way you make it work, simple as that. I want my life to be primitive, so here I am. You know why you feel like you’re not supposed to be here? Because you don’t even know what kind of life you want to live."
    s1 "生活就是按照你的方式運作的，就這麼簡單。我認為生活是原始的，所以我在這裡。你知道你為什麼覺得你不應該在這裡嗎？因為你甚至不知道自己想過什麼樣的生活。"

# game/room.rpy:1117
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_cb55d00a:

    # e1 "I… well…"
    e1 "我……嗯……"

# game/room.rpy:1119
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_6c2834b6:

    # s1 "Don’t worry, Hermes. Let me take care of it. Let me comfort you, my dear, so you could forget about everything else."
    s1 "沒關系的，赫耳墨斯。讓我替你處理這件事。讓我來安慰你，親愛的，以便你可以忘記其他的一切。"

# game/room.rpy:1121
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5615a6d3:

    # m1 "No way!"
    m1 "不可能吧！"

# game/room.rpy:1122
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d4ed5509:

    # e1 "Hey, what just happened? Where did Sophie go?"
    e1 "嗨，剛剛發生什麼事情？索菲又去哪兒呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1124
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f8af7a15:

    # m1 "I got rid of that succubus."
    m1 "我擺脫了那個女妖。"

# game/room.rpy:1126
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5be7b092:

    # m1 "Hey, stay with me, Hermes. I’ve seen the future, and it’s not the best one, I admit… now we’ll have a second chance to make it great."
    m1 "誒，你跟我一起吧，赫耳墨斯。我承認，我看到了未來，但這不是最好的未來。現在，我們將有另一次機會來實現美好的未來。"

# game/room.rpy:1127
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_14657251_1:

    # e1 "What are we going to do?"
    e1 "咱們要做什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:1129
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_b5e504d0:

    # m1 "We’re going to believe in tomorrow. If you think you’re not supposed to be here, make tomorrow the place to be. Please… do it for me"
    m1 "咱們要相信明天。要是你認為你不應該在這裡，那就去你心中的明天。拜托……就算為了我。"

# game/room.rpy:1131
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_f9c9172a:

    # e1 "Will you love me?"
    e1 "你會愛我嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:1133
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_17a917c3:

    # m1 "I’ll love the you of tomorrow, I promise."
    m1 "我保証我一定會愛明天的你。"

# game/room.rpy:1135
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5cf9fa4c:

    # "I try to push the button, but nothing happens. Maybe I should try tomorrow."
    "我嘗試按下按鈕，可是什麼都沒有發生。我也許應該明天再次試一下。"

# game/room.rpy:1140
translate chinese_trad close_game_02a0c651:

    # "Okay, I had enough... I should think of a proper way to give feedback on this masterpiece."
    "好吧，我受夠了……我應該想出一種適當的方式來反饋這部杰作。"

# game/room.rpy:1146
translate chinese_trad close_game_done_5cf9fa4c:

    # "I try to push the button, but nothing happens. Maybe I should try tomorrow."
    "我嘗試按下按鈕，可是什麼都沒發生。我也許應該明天再嘗試一下。"

# game/room.rpy:1165
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_3aae40ef:

    # "Man, I'm beat."
    "天哪，我被打敗了。"

# game/room.rpy:1166
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_a73a474b:

    # "My mind still goes over what I heard on the way home."
    "我腦海中還是在考慮回家的路上聽到的那句話。"

# game/room.rpy:1167
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_128fa27b:

    # "Never judge the book by its cover, right?"
    "永遠不要以貌取人，是吧？"

# game/room.rpy:1168
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_eca482cd:

    # "Should I give Ermy's game another go?"
    "我要不要再次試著玩葉爾米的游戲呢？"

# game/room.rpy:1169
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_dc694895:

    # "But first, let me check on my sister."
    "可是要先看看我的妹妹。"

# game/room.rpy:1171
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_68718e2a:

    # "I can't believe you came empty-handed again."
    "我簡直不敢相信你又空手來了。"

