    # imo "Get me some pictures, pictures of the girls you study with!"
    imo "你找到你喜歡的女孩子了嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:415
translate chinese_trad d2_random_imouto19_9a6427e2:

    # imo "Will you buy my a car when I grow up?"
    imo "你應該努力學習找一份比較好的工作，然后你才能給我買東西。"

# game/room.rpy:421
translate chinese_trad d2_random_imouto20_772b76eb:

    # imo "I want to go to the sea!"
    imo "給我買個新的游戲吧！已經沒興趣玩這一個。"

# game/room.rpy:427
translate chinese_trad d2_random_imouto21_2ddcfeed:

    # imo "Parents called again, they're kinda worried."
    imo "媽媽給我打電話說讓我監督你。"

# game/room.rpy:433
translate chinese_trad d2_random_imouto22_08c29d5e:

    # imo "What are we going to have for dinner?"
    imo "你有沒有給我買一點什麼？"

# game/room.rpy:439
translate chinese_trad d2_random_imouto23_bfb9c1be:

    # imo "Do you want to play with me?"
    imo "我渴了。"

# game/room.rpy:445
translate chinese_trad d2_random_imouto24_5ea9111c:

    # imo "You should clean your bathroom!"
    imo "我累了。"

# game/room.rpy:451
translate chinese_trad d2_random_imouto25_c2b7092e:

    # imo "I'm staying with you forever!"
    imo "我不想飛回去。"

# game/room.rpy:459
translate chinese_trad d2_random_imouto_last_a8e3ac08:

    # imo "Still doing nothing? Fine! I'm not talking to you anymore!"
    imo "你又無所事事的嗎？好吧！我不再跟你說話了！"

# game/room.rpy:475
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d1_e04b6578:

    # imo "Hey, did you buy anythig tasty for me?"
    imo "嘿，你有給我買好吃的嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:476
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d1_0297f312:

    # imo "By the way, a strange girl came and left something for you. It's on your table."
    imo "喔，順便說一下，一個奇怪的女孩子過來給你留了個東西。它在你桌子上。"

# game/room.rpy:477
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d1_4d4f079b:

    # imo "Was this your classmate? She left so quickly!"
    imo "她是你的同學嗎？她很快就走了！"

# game/room.rpy:478
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d1_8610bf63:

    # imo "Her ears were so weird!"
    imo "她的耳朵非常奇怪！"

# game/room.rpy:479
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d1_4ddcb638:

    # imo "When're you going to buy a new console? This one is {i}old{/i}"
    imo "你什麼時候打算買新的機器呢？這個真舊。"

# game/room.rpy:521
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/room.rpy:524
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e81031bf:

    # ermy_game "\"I don’t think I’m supposed to be here.\""
    ermy_game "\"我覺得我不應該在這裡。\""

# game/room.rpy:530
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ae976785:

    # nvl clear
    # ermy_game "Strangely enough, soon my body got used to being deprived of sleep. I drastically cut down my calorie intake as a next step – this also allowed me to become quite slim, it concentrated me, one hundred percent, on food and food only, regardless of how tired I was. Meat. Fish. Pasta. Pizza. I could smell each of these words…"
    nvl clear
    ermy_game "奇怪的是，我的身體很快地適應失眠的狀況。然后，我把攝入的熱量大大減少作為下一步。再說，這也讓我變得很瘦。無論我多麼困，這也幫我把100％注意力唯一集中到食物。肉。魚。意大利面。披薩。每個詞我都能聞一聞……"

# game/room.rpy:537
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_395fee53:

    # nvl clear
    # ermy_game "However, they fed me so well at the training camp that my silly mind decided to think again. So annoying, I’m telling you! And there was no stopping it… A phone started to ring in my head from time to time, driving me crazy. I know that as soon as I pick it up, I’d hear the same phrase…"
    nvl clear
    ermy_game "可是，當我在軍訓營的時候，吃得那麼多我的腦子又開始想了。真糟糕 我告訴你！一開始想了，就不可能停止。在我腦海裡，電話響起來了。我知道我要是接這個電話，就會聽到……"

# game/room.rpy:544
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_e20c1c8b:

    # nvl clear
    # ermy_game "They looked like they wanted to tell me something, but all I could hear was that annoying buzz. Or maybe it sounded more like a distorted phone call… doesn’t matter though."
    nvl clear
    ermy_game "他們看來想跟我說些什麼，可是我所聽到的隻有那種讓人火大的嗡嗡聲。或者，它可能更像是一種電話響……無所謂了。"

# game/room.rpy:552
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/room.rpy:563
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_383636ae:

    # ee "A young woman appears seemingly out of nowhere. Dressed in an overly tight nurse uniform, she carries a syringe filled with a strange, bright liquid."
    ee "一個年輕的女孩子不知從什麼地方冒了出來。身上穿著過分緊的護士服飾，她拿著一支含有奇怪的亮色的液體的注射器。"

# game/room.rpy:572
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_df2dc478:

    # ee "I thought back to my military training… The best way to deal with mentally unstable people is to take them seriously."
    ee "我回想了一下我的軍訓。對待精神不穩定的人最好方法就是讓他們認真起來。"

# game/room.rpy:579
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_6293d535:

    # ee "She moves closer, and I can’t help but notice that the button on Sophie’s blouse is about to be ripped off by her… well…"
    ee "她走得更近了，我不由自主地注意到蘇菲上衣上的紐扣就要被她扯掉了……。"

# game/room.rpy:594
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9f1f1f9d:

    # ee "This room gets more crowded, now that a second girl, wrapped up in a latex costume serving presumably no other purpose rather than an aesthetic one, shows up in front of me."
    ee "第二個女孩兒進來了站在我前面時，房間就變得更加擁擠。她穿著一套好像隻為審美服務的乳膠服裝。"

# game/room.rpy:617
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_49075dd6:

    # ee "The second I say that the phone starts ringing again. Ring-ring… ring-ring… like those machines in old detective phones."
    ee "我說這句話的時候，電話一下子就開始響了。鈴鈴……鈴鈴……似乎那些就電影一樣。"

# game/room.rpy:619
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_6932f0a0:

    # ee "The sound becomes more and more loud. My head hurts! Someone should stop it. Pick up the phone, please…"
    ee "聲音越來越大。我的頭疼！有人應該別讓它響了。接電話，拜托……"

# game/room.rpy:644
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8242434b:

    # ee "Sophie shivers and stops talking."
    ee "索菲打著哆嗦不再說了。"

# game/room.rpy:652
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_a2c7abae:

    # ee "A cute girl, dressed in a maid outfit, joins the conversation. Where was she hiding? Weird… By the way, she holds a plushie in one hand."
    ee "一個穿著一套女仆服的漂亮的女孩兒加入對話。她以前在哪兒藏著呢？奇怪……再說，她手裡拿著一個毛絨玩具。"

# game/room.rpy:663
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8d206a1b:

    # ee "Ring-ring…"
    ee "鈴鈴……"

# game/room.rpy:713
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d49564e5:

    # ee "I’m quite sure she’s referring to that plushie."
    ee "我很確定她指的是那個毛絨玩具。"

# game/room.rpy:723
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_91e9c136:

    # ee "And she was right."
    ee "原來，她是對的。"

# game/room.rpy:850
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_ca9491f8:

    # ee "So we did."
    ee "我們就談了小貓。"

# game/room.rpy:927
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_8da00748:

    # ee "I too agreed with that. However, nothing happened."
    ee "我也同意了這句話，但是，什麼都沒發生。"

# game/room.rpy:931
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_7db20d8b:

    # ee "She moves so swiftly. It doesn’t even hurt… My vision starts to become blurry."
    ee "她迅速行動了。甚至都不疼。我的視力模糊了起來。"

# game/room.rpy:934
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_bf2f7a0d:

    # ee "Ring-ring. The phone rings again, but this time I manage to answer it, somehow."
    ee "鈴鈴。電話再次響起，但是這次我設法以某種方式接聽電話。"

# game/room.rpy:935
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9ae1ae91:

    # ee "The guy on the other end of the line tells me that if I die, I’ll stay in this room forever. Uhm… why haven’t I thought about it before?"
    ee "打電話的那家伙跟我說要是我死亡，就會永遠留在這個房間。哼……我怎麼以前沒想到這個呢？"

# game/room.rpy:936
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_2b6f9836:

    # ee "I’m afraid it’s too late now."
    ee "恐怕現在已經太晚了。"

# game/room.rpy:940
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_761e2296:

    # ee "\"Love\""
    ee "\"愛情\""

# game/room.rpy:956
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0c7888ba:

    # ee "Two other girls appear right in front of my eyes."
    ee "兩個其他的女孩子突然出現就在我眼前。"

# game/room.rpy:978
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_701124c6:

    # ee "Silence was her answer."
    ee "沉默是她的答案。"

# game/room.rpy:982
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_2b75df09:

    # ee "She spanks me with her plushie."
    ee "她用她的玩具打我的屁股。"

# game/room.rpy:984
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_3f6c2965:

    # ee "I notice Sophie and Megan staring at me."
    ee "我發現索菲和梅根盯著我看。"

# game/room.rpy:1038
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_454940ca:

    # ee "She does a few quick swings, and shortly after that we’re the only ones standing in the room."
    ee "她快速擺了幾步，不久之后，我們是唯一站在房間裡的人。"

# game/room.rpy:1043
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_d47ffec2:

    # ee "I feel cold sweat dripping down my back. Sophie’s clearly bonkers, and I need to calm her down somehow."
    ee "我感覺到冷汗從我的背上流下來。索菲顯然是傻子，我需要以某種方式使她平靜下來。"

# game/room.rpy:1057
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_9e436be0:

    # ee "Swing! The needle bites me like a snake. My legs start to tremble."
    ee "針就像蛇一樣咬了我。我的腿開始發抖。"

# game/room.rpy:1069
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_5a644da7:

    # ee "I’m back from the dead, it seems. Even more, the usual crowd’s here, as if nothing happened at all. The phone starts ringing again."
    ee "看來，我復活了。再說，那些老伙計也都在，似乎什麼都沒發生。電話又響起來了。"

# game/room.rpy:1070
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_0973f330:

    # ee "I don’t think I can get rid of that pain in my head, so I badly need to concentrate on something else… maybe small talk can help."
    ee "好像我不能擺脫頭痛，所以我非常需要專注於其他東西……聊天也許能有幫助。"

# game/room.rpy:1078
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_2ec0ee81:

    # ee "You’re kidding me. Have they entirely forgotten about what happened before?"
    ee "你一定是開玩笑。她們難道把所有以前發生的事情都忘了嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:1115
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_532099d4:

    # ee "Her annoyance doesn’t seem to be justified at the very slightest, but I’m not surprised, as it fits perfectly with the weird ambiance of that place."
    ee "她的生氣看來一點道理也沒有，我可不吃驚。它正好符合這個地方奇怪的氣氛。"

# game/room.rpy:1142
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_740098a8:

    # s1 "You guys don’t even know about the right reason to hate everyone around you. I mean… they exist. They smell, they take space, they’re loud and annoying."
    s1 "你們甚至不知道恨周圍每個人的正當理由。我是說……他們存在。他們呼吸、佔用空間、他們吵到讓人心煩"
# game/room.rpy:1143
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d1_aff9eaa8:

    # s1 "That’s why I always stay in my lab, so I could have some personal space. But even there, when I visit the bathroom, I look in the mirror and realize I’m no different."
    s1 "這就是為什麼我一直呆在實驗室裡的原因，所以我可以有一些個人空間。但是即使在那兒，當我去洗手間時，我看著鏡子，也意識到自己沒有什麼不同。"


# game/room.rpy:1308
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_553dedac:

    # imo "I can't believe you came empty-handed again."
    imo "我簡直不敢相信你又空手來了。"

# game/room.rpy:1309
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_340597f8:

    # imo1 "That girl from yesterday came again, saying she needs to check on your progress."
    imo1 "昨天來過的那個女孩子今天又來了，說她需查一下你的進度。"

# game/room.rpy:1310
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_0a61f002:

    # imo "I replied that you can handle everything yourself."
    imo "我就跟她說你能夠自己打理所有的一切。"

# game/room.rpy:1311
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d2_86347a80:

    # imo "By the way, what was in that document she gave you?"
    imo "順便說一下，她給你的文件是什麼內容？"

# game/room.rpy:1344
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d2_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/room.rpy:1346
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d2_b0d17d0d:

    # ermy_game "I’m in this room again, the girls staring at me, awaiting eagerly what’s going to happen next."
    ermy_game "我又在這個房間裡，女孩子們盯著看我，熱切盼望著下一個會發生什麼事情。"

# game/room.rpy:1353
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d2_c75f475d:

    # nvl clear
    # ermy_game "What did I want to say with all this? Who’s going to read it? Man… I wanted this game to be exciting, but it’s so boring. The characters, I’ve seen them all countless times… a random bunch of characters thrown together in one room. My game is empty. I am empty."
    nvl clear
    ermy_game "我想對所有這些說些什麼？誰會看這些？天哪……我原來想這個游戲會讓人激動，它可真沒意思呢。我無數次看到過這些角色……隨意的一群人都一起被放在一個房間裡。我的游戲是空虛的。我是空虛的。"

# game/room.rpy:1361
translate chinese_trad ermy_game_d2_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/room.rpy:1381
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d3_7714a930:

    # imo "Your face is all red!"
    imo "你的臉都紅了！"

# game/room.rpy:1382
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d3_2f86c619:

    # imo "Are you okay?"
    imo "你身體好嗎？"

# game/room.rpy:1383
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d3_7aa1715f:

    # imo "Tomorrow is Friday, will you spent time with me?"
    imo "明天是周五，你能不能跟我一起呆一點時間？"

# game/room.rpy:1384
translate chinese_trad sweet_home_d3_502bc282:

    # imo "By the way, that girl came yet again!"
    imo "順便說，那個女孩子又來了！"

